parameters.description:
A json object . likelyToMove {
min (integer, optional): Finds only people whose likely to move score is above the specified value. Accepted values between 0 and 100 ,

max (integer, optional): Finds only people whose likely to move score is below the specified value. Accepted values between 0 and 100 ,

boostExclusive (boolean, optional): If true, uses "exclusive" matching on candidates who are likely to move. Otherwise, the default "inclusive" matching is used.
}

